me.bristermitten.privatemines.config.menu

Class MenuSpec

  • java.lang.Object
    • me.bristermitten.privatemines.config.menu.MenuSpec

  • public class MenuSpec
extends java.lang.Object
    A specification for a Menu. This is sort of like a template, and can be copied for placeholders in each item.

    The general pattern is that 1 MenuSpec holds the actual "raw" data from the config, and the rest are copied and have placeholders applied.

    For an example see PrivateMineMenu
